<div id="article-container">
<h1 id="content-title">Lace Them Up: How to Stop Pain With Shoelaces</h1>				

<div class="dek">The fixes for four common foot issues may be as simple as re-lacing your shoes.</div><div class="share">
<div id="facebookLike"></div>
